@startuml DappVote Three-Tier System Architecture

actor User

package "Presentation Layer" {
  [Next.js UI]
}

package "Logic Layer" {
  [Authentication Service]
  [Blockchain Service]
}

package "Database Layer" {
  database "MongoDB" {
    [User Data]
  }
  
  database "Blockchain" {
    [DappVotes Smart Contract]
  }
}

' Core interactions with correct data flow
User --> [Next.js UI] : Interacts
[Next.js UI] --> [Authentication Service] : Auth Requests
[Next.js UI] --> [Blockchain Service] : Vote Operations
[Authentication Service] --> [User Data] : Validates/Stores
[Blockchain Service] --> [DappVotes Smart Contract] : Executes Transactions

@enduml 